author: CBR
description:
Marvel vs DC power rankings return as leaked trailers, MCU marketing doubts, and DC momentum collide in our hype list for 2026 and beyond.

On this episode of CBR's Heroes Journey Podcast, Sean O'Connell and Sierra Nutkevitch discuss a leaked Spider-Man: Brand New Day trailer circulating online in near-pristine quality, and what that says about studios losing control of their biggest releases. From there, they break down their updated Marvel vs DC power rankings across 16 upcoming projects, and the big takeaway is the confidence shift.

Marvel's biggest event films spark the most debate, especially as Secret Wars brings new fears and Doomsday raises serious questions. Meanwhile, DC's slate gains energy with the Supergirl trailer push and the continued rise of Gunn's next Superman chapter.

Chapters:
00:08 – Spider-Man Brand New Day Leak and Trailer Piracy
03:05 – 2026+ Marvel vs DC Power Rankings Explained
04:29 – Jimmy Olsen, Vision Quest, Marvel Zombies & More
06:31 – Avengers Secre
title: Marvel vs DC Power Rankings: The Hype Gap Is Getting Real | Heroes Journey Podcast EP 12
